This is an exercise that I did for a job interview in August 2015. The task was to programatically invoke Cassandra DB's stress tool and to record a few metrics at periodic intervals. This project makes use of multi-ithreading and Java Management Extensions (JMX).

abstract.doc - The description of the project files
console_output.txt - The output to the console as the test ran
JMXmetrics.html - The test results
